<item>
            <title>[LU-201] unregistered bulk after reply unregistered causes &quot;ptlrpc_set_wait&quot; to hang</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-201</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;in ptlrpc_set_wait,  the bulk is not unregistered if the reply was unregistered asynchronously, and the phase of the request was also changed into&lt;br/&gt;
 &quot;RQ_PHASE_UNREGISTERING&quot;,   which causes the &quot;ptlrpc_set_wait&quot; to hang for the bulk&apos;s state remains to be active (bulk-&amp;gt;bd_network_rw == 1)&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="10566">LU-201</key>
